{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a43e3e01c1","title":"日前形势和战略方针问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93c806ad05","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"a43e3e01c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"beb7cd5a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"日前形势和战略方针问题！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1"},{"id":"b20bb035ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月9日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1"},{"id":"3ce3c39d3e","type":"paragraph","text":"根据二、四方面军北上，西南事变发展，日本对绥蒙进攻等情况，我们认为兄部须立即准备配合红军选定九、十月间有利时机决心发动抗日局面，而以占领兰州、打通苏联、巩固内部、出兵绥远为基本战略方针。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1"},{"id":"4c019cfd6d","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石一解决西南问题，就有极大可能进攻西北。无论如何兄不要再去南京了，并要十分防备蒋的暗害阴谋。目前此点关系全局，卫队的成分应加考查，要放在政治上可靠的干部手中","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1"},{"id":"32d29527d2","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和洛甫（张闻天）、周恩来、博古（秦邦宪）关于目前形势和战略方针问题致张学良电的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1"}],"page":{"id":"93f4132379","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a43e3e01c1","start":41,"end":41}}}},"__N_SSG":true}